title: Jason Kelce and the Championship Parade, the 49ers' Jimmy G. Signing, and the Josh McDaniels Fallout | GM Street (Ep. 236)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss Jason Kelce calling out Lombardi and the media (00:30), the effectiveness of the "Vienna offense" in the Super Bowl (02:30), a monster contract for Jimmy Garoppolo (10:30), the Josh McDaniels drama (16:00), and Matt Patricia kicking off his career in Detroit (31:30).
